  <entry>
    <title>Insert Videos and Picture in Hexo</title>
    <link href="https://fdujyy.github.io/2018/10/18/insert-local-picture-in-hexo/"/>
    <id>https://fdujyy.github.io/2018/10/18/insert-local-picture-in-hexo/</id>
    <published>2018-10-18T07:24:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-10-18T08:31:30.248Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Modify-Config-and-Install-Plugin"><a href="#Modify-Config-and-Install-Plugin" class="headerlink" title="Modify Config and Install Plugin"></a>Modify Config and Install Plugin</h1><p>Set <code>post_asset_folder: true</code> in <code>_config.yml</code>. When you create a new post using <code>hexo new post_name</code> it will create a new foler named <code>post_name</code> besides <code>post_name.md</code>.</p><p>Install <code>hexo-asset-image</code> plugin:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>Modify <code>hexo-asset-image</code> plugin in <code>node_modules\hexo-asset-image\index.js</code>: </p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$(<span class="string">'img'</span>).each(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> src = $(<span class="keyword">this</span>).attr(<span class="string">'src'</span>).replace(<span class="string">'\\'</span>, <span class="string">'/'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    src = <span class="string">'/'</span>+src.split(<span class="string">'/'</span>)[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="comment">//Add this line</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(!<span class="regexp">/http[s]*.*|\/\/.*/</span>.test(src))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> linkArray = link.split(<span class="string">'/'</span>).filter(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">elem</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> elem != <span class="string">''</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> srcArray = src.split(<span class="string">'/'</span>).filter(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">elem</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> elem != <span class="string">''</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(linkArray[linkArray.length - <span class="number">1</span>] == srcArray[<span class="number">0</span>])</span><br><span class="line">        srcArray.shift();</span><br><span class="line">        src = srcArray.join(<span class="string">'/'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        $(<span class="keyword">this</span>).attr(<span class="string">'src'</span>, <span class="string">'/'</span> + link + src);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><p>Add <code>src = &#39;/&#39;+src.split(&#39;/&#39;)[1]</code> to remove the folder name in the generated link.</p><h1 id="Insert-Local-Picture-in-Your-Post"><a href="#Insert-Local-Picture-in-Your-Post" class="headerlink" title="Insert Local Picture in Your Post"></a>Insert Local Picture in Your Post</h1><p>Put your local picture in the folder hexo creates and insert it in your post by <code>![image text](path/to/your/picture &#39;image caption&#39;)</code>. Here is an example:<br><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">img missing</span>](<span class="link">2018-10-18-insert-local-picture-in-hexo/federer-usopen-preview-2018-friday.jpg 'Roger Federer'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="/2018/10/18/insert-local-picture-in-hexo/federer-usopen-preview-2018-friday.jpg" alt="img missing" title="Roger Federer"></p><h1 id="Insert-Videos"><a href="#Insert-Videos" class="headerlink" title="Insert Videos"></a>Insert Videos</h1><p>Copy code from video sites and paste to your post. For example:<br><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">720</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">1280</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">'http://player.youku.com/embed/XMjgzNzM0NTYxNg=='</span> <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">0</span> <span class="attr">allowfullscreen</span>=<span class="string">'always'</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><iframe height="720" width="1280" src="http://player.youku.com/embed/XMjgzNzM0NTYxNg==" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="always"></iframe><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"1280"</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">"720"</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://www.youtube.com/embed/f8YEiCAPAbg"</span> <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attr">allow</span>=<span class="string">"autoplay; encrypted-media"</span> <span class="attr">allowfullscreen</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><iframe width="1280" height="720" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/f8YEiCAPAbg" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h1 id="Enjoy-yourself"><a href="#Enjoy-yourself" class="headerlink" title="Enjoy yourself!"></a>Enjoy yourself!</h1>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h1 id=&quot;Modify-Config-and-Install-Plugin&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Modify-Config-and-Install-Plugin&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Modify Config and Install Plugin&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Modify Config and Install Plugin&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Set &lt;code&gt;post_asset_folder: true&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;_config.yml&lt;/code&gt;. When you create a new post using &lt;code&gt;hexo new post_name&lt;/code&gt; it will create a new foler named &lt;code&gt;post_name&lt;/code&gt; besides &lt;code&gt;post_name.md&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Install &lt;code&gt;hexo-asset-image&lt;/code&gt; plugin:&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight bash&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;npm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image --save&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Modify &lt;code&gt;hexo-asset-image&lt;/code&gt; plugin in &lt;code&gt;node_modules\hexo-asset-image\index.js&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight js&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;img&#39;&lt;/span&gt;).each(&lt;span class=&quot;function&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;params&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#123;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; src = $(&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;).attr(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;src&#39;&lt;/span&gt;).replace(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;\\&#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    src = &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;+src.split(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;)[&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span class=&quot;comment&quot;&gt;//Add this line&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;(!&lt;span class=&quot;regexp&quot;&gt;/http[s]*.*|\/\/.*/&lt;/span&gt;.test(src))&amp;#123;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; linkArray = link.split(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;).filter(&lt;span class=&quot;function&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;params&quot;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#123;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; elem != &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;&#39;&lt;/span&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &amp;#125;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; srcArray = src.split(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;).filter(&lt;span class=&quot;function&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;params&quot;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#123;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; elem != &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;&#39;&lt;/span&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &amp;#125;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;(linkArray[linkArray.length - &lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] == srcArray[&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        srcArray.shift();&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        src = srcArray.join(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        $(&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;).attr(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;src&#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt; + link + src);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    &amp;#125;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&amp;#125;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
